Mr. Rad.

15:50.542 --> 15:53.221
I just hope we can repay you
by making regionals.

15:53.502 --> 15:55.482
Uh, I thought
this was regionals.

15:56.092 --> 15:58.715
Don't let my confusion
undercut their importance.

15:58.750 --> 15:59.833
Places, everyone!

16:02.337 --> 16:04.588
Scooch, scooch, scooch,
scooch, scooch.

16:04.622 --> 16:05.806
I could not have done this

16:05.840 --> 16:07.123
without your
recruiting skills, Abed.

16:07.141 --> 16:08.792
I was happy to do it.
For a while there, I thought

16:08.810 --> 16:11.294
we were gonna end the semester
on a really dark note.

16:11.312 --> 16:12.729
I'm glad we're singing
and dancing together instead.

16:12.764 --> 16:14.064
This has been a good time.

16:14.098 --> 16:16.066
And it's going to continue
to be a good time.

16:16.100 --> 16:18.735
If we win regionals, then it's
straight on to sectionals.

16:18.770 --> 16:21.238
And then a week later is semis.
Then semiregionals.

16:21.272 --> 16:23.073
Then regional-semis.

16:23.107 --> 16:25.542
Then national
lower-zone semis!

16:25.577 --> 16:27.277
Oh.

16:27.311 --> 16:28.912
But I kinda thought this was...

16:28.947 --> 16:30.831
You know, just for Christmas.

16:30.865 --> 16:32.716
No, no, no.

16:32.750 --> 16:34.918
This is forever.

16:34.953 --> 16:37.337
This is what we do now.

16:37.372 --> 16:40.390
This is who we are.

