17:38.416 --> 17:41.885
♪ Christmas time ♪

17:41.919 --> 17:42.886
♪ me so Christmas,
me so merry ♪

17:42.904 --> 17:45.355
No, stop, stop, stop, stop!

17:45.389 --> 17:47.057
What are you doing?
Get off the stage!

17:47.075 --> 17:48.492
I'm singing my heart's song.

17:48.526 --> 17:50.861
Get off the stage,
and never sing again!

17:50.895 --> 17:51.995
You are the worst!

17:52.030 --> 17:53.113
Hey!

17:53.164 --> 17:55.232
You do not get to call Britta
"the worst."

17:55.266 --> 17:58.234
