is an all-inclusive school.

18:02.340 --> 18:05.459
Why don't we let Britta
sing her awkward song?

18:05.510 --> 18:07.744
Yeah!

18:07.762 --> 18:10.080
No, no, no, no, no, no!

18:10.098 --> 18:13.884
